Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: auto-tqdm
Version: 1.0.0
Summary: Wrapper over tqdm for automatically handle switch between jupyter and cli and tunes bar to my liking (automatic resizing, stronger smoothing and tuning for erratic iterations).
Home-page: https://github.com/LucaCappelletti94/auto_tqdm
Author: Luca Cappelletti
Author-email: cappelletti.luca94@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: auto_tqdm
        =============================================================================
        |travis| |sonar_quality| |sonar_maintainability| |sonar_coverage| |code_climate_maintainability| |pip|
        
        Wrapper over tqdm for automatically handle switch between jupyter notebook and cli and tunes bar to my liking (automatic resizing, stronger smoothing and tuning for erratic iterations).
        
        How do I get this?
        ----------------------------------
        As usual, just run pip:
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            pip install auto_tqdm
        
